        description:
          '<p><strong>Bioderma Sensibio</strong></p><p>Sensibio H20 is dermatologically approved micellar water that works on all skin types; its fatty acid esters, which are the basic components of micelles, are almost like the phospholipids of the cell membrane and thus helps in constructing that skin\u2019s hydrolipidic layer.&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Bioderma Micellar water&nbsp;</strong></p><p>In the morning, this cleanser can be used for facial cleansing, while at night, it can be utilized as a makeup remover. It can be used daily for getting rid of dirt and makeup, with the help of micellar water, minus the excessive drying of the skin.</p><p><strong>Cutaneous and ocular tolerance</strong></p><p>Micellar water has the best skin and ocular tolerance. It does not cause any reactions to the skin.&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Bioderma Sensibio H2O effective and gentle&nbsp;</strong></p><p>The concept is easy; micellar water works in removing contaminants, makeup residues, and oil with a few strokes. Nonstop scrubbing and rubbing are not required to attain fresh-looking skin, free of dirt and impurities.&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Bioderma Skincare</strong></p><p>Micellar water is made with gentle formula and is excellent to use in your regular skincare routine. After using this, your skin will look fresh, healthy, and glowing as it cleans all the dirt and dust particles in the skin.&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Highest quality ingredients</strong></p><p>It is made with the highest quality and 100% pure ingredients. It contains no harmful or reactive chemicals. It is free from phthalates and parabens. It is hypoallergenic. It is free from alcohol and fragrances.&nbsp;</p><p><strong>How to use it?</strong></p><p>Take a cotton pad and soak the pad in the sensibio water.&nbsp;</p><p>Gently clean your face by applying the soaked cotton to your face and eyes. You can remove makeup also.&nbsp;</p><p>For proper cleansing, reapply the cotton until the pad becomes clean.&nbsp;</p><p>After cleansing, dab the face with a soft towel. Do not rub.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>',
